=== As Mogho Naba of Oubritenga === The first capitol of [[Oubritenga Province|Oubritenga]] ("Oubri's land") was Guilongou, near modern-day [[Ziniaré]],{{sfn|Rupley|Bangali|Diamitani|2013|p=156}} but typically moved to a village preferred by each new king upon his accession.{{sfn|Levtzion|1975|p=186}}
